<tree expanded="true" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" root="false"><frontmatter> <anchor>221</anchor>  <taxon>Definition</taxon> <addr>axt-000R</addr>  <route>axt-000R.xml</route> <date><year>2023</year> <month>9</month> <day>15</day></date>  <title>Compact space (point-set)</title> </frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>  A space <tex>X</tex> is called <em>compact</em> if for every <link href="axt-000S.xml" type="local" title="Open covering (point-set)">open covering</link>  <tex>X =  \bigcup _{i  \in  I} U_i</tex> of it, there is a subset <tex>J  \subseteq  I</tex> such
  that <tex>\{  U_j  \} _{j  \in  J}</tex> is also an <link href="axt-000S.xml" type="local" title="Open covering (point-set)">open covering</link> of <tex>X</tex>.
</p></mainmatter> <backmatter><contributions/> <context/> <related><tree expanded="false" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" root="false"><frontmatter> <anchor>222</anchor>  <taxon>Definition</taxon> <addr>axt-000S</addr>  <route>axt-000S.xml</route> <date><year>2023</year> <month>9</month> <day>15</day></date>  <title>Open covering (point-set)</title> </frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>  A family <tex>\{  U_i  \} _{i  \in  I}</tex> of opens of space <tex>X</tex> is said to be an <em>open
  covering</em> for a subset <tex>A  \subseteq  X</tex> if
  <tex display="block">A =  \bigcup _{i  \in  I} U_i.</tex></p></mainmatter> </tree></related> <backlinks><tree expanded="false" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" root="false"><frontmatter> <anchor>223</anchor>   <addr>axt-000W</addr>  <route>axt-000W.xml</route> <date><year>2023</year> <month>9</month> <day>15</day></date>  <title>Compactness and the finite intersection property</title> </frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>  A space <tex>X</tex> is <link href="axt-000R.xml" type="local" title="Compact space (point-set)">compact</link> iff for every family <tex>\{  F_i  \} _{i  \in   I}</tex> of closed sets having the finite intersection property, the intersection
  <tex>\bigcap _{i  \in  I} F_i</tex> is nonempty.
</p></mainmatter> </tree></backlinks> <references/></backmatter></tree>